  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introduction to Play</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four color jumps is a casual jumping game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players need to move the small ball in the operation screen through the left and right keys to make the small ball rise, pass through or contact the springboard and jump up constantly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/226c3b686d759ce59bb7bb6f027f8888.poster.avif?t=1768035204\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/226c3b686d759ce59bb7bb6f027f8888.webm?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/226c3b686d759ce59bb7bb6f027f8888.mp4?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the default white, the springboard has four colors. Each time you pass an obstacle, you will change the color. When you encounter the springboard with the same color as the ball, the jump range will be higher than usual~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gold coins settled after passing the level can unlock skin and other rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/450d686ebad275872479331030f06f23.poster.avif?t=1768035204\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/450d686ebad275872479331030f06f23.webm?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/450d686ebad275872479331030f06f23.mp4?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operation guide</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A, D or ←→ key to control the movement of the small ball</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/47a36f7ff3d0a83cc1bb7806737c7ced.poster.avif?t=1768035204\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/47a36f7ff3d0a83cc1bb7806737c7ced.webm?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/47a36f7ff3d0a83cc1bb7806737c7ced.mp4?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press \"2\" and \"5\" at the top of the letter area of the keyboard at the same time on the interface of selecting a level to temporarily unlock the level.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Introduction to Play</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four color jumps is a casual jumping game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players need to move the small ball in the operation screen through the left and right keys to make the small ball rise, pass through or contact the springboard and jump up constantly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/226c3b686d759ce59bb7bb6f027f8888.poster.avif?t=1768035204\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/226c3b686d759ce59bb7bb6f027f8888.webm?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/226c3b686d759ce59bb7bb6f027f8888.mp4?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In addition to the default white, the springboard has four colors. Each time you pass an obstacle, you will change the color. When you encounter the springboard with the same color as the ball, the jump range will be higher than usual~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gold coins settled after passing the level can unlock skin and other rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/450d686ebad275872479331030f06f23.poster.avif?t=1768035204\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/450d686ebad275872479331030f06f23.webm?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/450d686ebad275872479331030f06f23.mp4?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Operation guide</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A, D or ←→ key to control the movement of the small ball</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/47a36f7ff3d0a83cc1bb7806737c7ced.poster.avif?t=1768035204\" width=600 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/47a36f7ff3d0a83cc1bb7806737c7ced.webm?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1656640/extras/47a36f7ff3d0a83cc1bb7806737c7ced.mp4?t=1768035204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press \"2\" and \"5\" at the top of the letter area of the keyboard at the same time on the interface of selecting a level to temporarily unlock the level.</p>",
